# Summary
This documentation details Amplitude's Mailchimp event streaming integration, which allows forwarding Amplitude events and users to Mailchimp. It covers the setup process, credential configuration, mapping requirements, event forwarding settings (with limitations for anonymous users), and user forwarding options that require pre-created Mailchimp merge fields.

